      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "{% comment %} Jaysou's FAQ {% endcomment %}\n<style>\n  .js-faq {\n    background: #FFFFFF;\n    padding: 110px 24px;\n  }\n  .js-faq-heading {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    font-size: 48px;\n    line-height: 1.05;\n    color: #1F1B17;\n    text-align: center;\n    margin: 0 auto 14px;\n    letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n  }\n  .js-faq-sub {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: rgba(31, 27, 23, 0.6);\n    margin: 0 auto 64px;\n    max-width: 520px;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    letter-spacing: 0.01em;\n  }\n  .js-faq-list {\n    max-width: 720px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n  .js-faq-item {\n    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(31, 27, 23, 0.15);\n  }\n  .js-faq-item:first-child {\n    border-top: 1px solid rgba(31, 27, 23, 0.15);\n  }\n  .js-faq-q {\n    cursor: pointer;\n    list-style: none;\n    padding: 28px 8px;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    color: #1F1B17;\n    transition: color 0.15s ease;\n    letter-spacing: 0.01em;\n  }\n  .js-faq-q::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }\n  .js-faq-q:hover { color: #8B6F4E; }\n  .js-faq-icon {\n    width: 16px;\n    height: 16px;\n    color: #1F1B17;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    margin-left: 16px;\n    transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n  }\n  .js-faq-item[open] .js-faq-icon {\n    transform: rotate(45deg);\n  }\n  .js-faq-a {\n    padding: 0 8px 28px;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    color: rgba(31, 27, 23, 0.7);\n    margin: 0;\n    max-width: 600px;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 749px) {\n    .js-faq { padding: 64px 16px; }\n    .js-faq-heading { font-size: 34px; }\n    .js-faq-q { font-size: 14px; padding: 22px 4px; }\n    .js-faq-a { font-size: 13px; padding: 0 4px 22px; }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"js-faq\">\n  <h2 class=\"js-faq-heading\">Questions</h2>\n  <p class=\"js-faq-sub\">Everything you'd want to know before applying.</p>\n  \n  <div class=\"js-faq-list\">\n    <details class=\"js-faq-item\">\n      <summary class=\"js-faq-q\">\n        How often should I use it?\n        <svg class=\"js-faq-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"5\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"19\"/><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/></svg>\n      </summary>\n      <p class=\"js-faq-a\">Once or twice a week. More frequently can over-dry the skin. Alternate with a hydrating mask for best results.</p>\n    </details>\n    \n    <details class=\"js-faq-item\">\n      <summary class=\"js-faq-q\">\n        Is it safe for sensitive skin?\n        <svg class=\"js-faq-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"5\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"19\"/><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/></svg>\n      </summary>\n      <p class=\"js-faq-a\">The PHA in the formula is gentler than typical AHA/BHA products, and guaiazulene calms while it works. Patch test on a small area first if your skin is very reactive.</p>\n    </details>\n    \n    <details class=\"js-faq-item\">\n      <summary class=\"js-faq-q\">\n        Will it really tighten pores?\n        <svg class=\"js-faq-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"5\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"19\"/><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/></svg>\n      </summary>\n      <p class=\"js-faq-a\">Pores are tightened visibly, not permanently. Regular use minimizes the appearance of pores by keeping them clean and free of buildup.</p>\n    </details>\n    \n    <details class=\"js-faq-item\">\n      <summary class=\"js-faq-q\">\n        Can I use it with retinol or other actives?\n        <svg class=\"js-faq-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"5\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"19\"/><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/></svg>\n      </summary>\n      <p class=\"js-faq-a\">Don't layer on the same day. Use the mask in the morning, retinol at night, or alternate days. Avoid combining with other exfoliants the same day.</p>\n    </details>\n    \n    <details class=\"js-faq-item\">\n      <summary class=\"js-faq-q\">\n        What does the blue tint do?\n        <svg class=\"js-faq-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"5\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"19\"/><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/></svg>\n      </summary>\n      <p class=\"js-faq-a\">It's guaiazulene — a calming compound derived from chamomile that gives the mask its color and helps soothe irritation while the clays and acids work.</p>\n    </details>\n    \n    <details class=\"js-faq-item\">\n      <summary class=\"js-faq-q\">\n        Do you ship outside Lebanon?\n        <svg class=\"js-faq-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"5\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"19\"/><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/></svg>\n      </summary>\n      <p class=\"js-faq-a\">Not yet. Jaysou's Skincare ships within Lebanon for $3 flat. We're focused on Beirut first.</p>\n    </details>\n    \n    <details class=\"js-faq-item\">\n      <summary class=\"js-faq-q\">\n        What if I don't love it?\n        <svg class=\"js-faq-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"5\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"19\"/><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/></svg>\n      </summary>\n      <p class=\"js-faq-a\">30-day returns. Send it back, full refund. No questions.</p>\n    </details>\n  </div>\n</div>",
        "full_width": false,
